  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "TRU COPY",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Stamford, Conn.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "October 5, 1956",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Mr. J. Edgar Hoover",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Director of F. B. I.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Enclosed is a copy of a Lecture sent to me from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Detroit. I think it is the most fascinating Research ever made.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "In your busy life you may not have encountered it,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "so I thought I would send you a copy.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Why doesn't the Government come out with the truth",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "about unidentified Flying Objects ?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Everybody seems to accept the \"Saucers\" as a matter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "of course, and people are becoming annoyed at the \"ostrich stance\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "our Leaders have taken about them.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "A number of clergymen feel that the time has come for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "someone to answer intelligently and sincerely the public's inquiries.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "They have gone to \"The Book\"--the Sacred Bible where man can always",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "find the answers to all his needs, doubts, fears--and inquiries!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "I have heard many people say that you probably have all",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "the answers--but I suppose you have been throttled too!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "I'm so glad you refused to accept the invitation to run",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "for President. You would have been a good one--(if you could be let",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "alone)--but sordid Party politics would have engulfed you too much.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "To the Legions of your admirers you stand too High--",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "are too clean and honest to become so involved.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Thanks to Almighty God there are character Influences",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "like you still standing on the same firm ground of our Forefathers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "Each day now a few more chips are knocked off the pillars",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "of Learning, High morals, decent behavior and honest standards. Where",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "can it all end? The days are becoming wearisome and fearful; surely the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "repercussions are shaking the outer walls of even Our Father's House.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "I wonder what the God of Our Fathers is going to do about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "it ?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "With deepest respect,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    }
  ],
  "blockCount": null
}
